    "description_long": "This is a single grave site featuring a polished gray stone base and a vertical black granite headstone. The headstone is inscribed with gold lettering, including a cross, a name, dates, and an epitaph in Polish. The grave is bordered by a slightly raised stone frame and is set on a rectangular tiled platform. A black cylindrical vase or candle holder is positioned near the head of the grave. The overall appearance is solemn and well-maintained, with the materials and design typical of modern European cemeteries.",
